node.text:
For #WorldRefugeeDay, I got the chance to swap stories of home with an incredible person. @mi.nnie_san lives in Denver, but was born in a refugee camp.⁣
⁣
It was a moving experience for me and a reminder that we all have a part to play making sure @refugees feel welcome.⁣
⁣
#WithRefugees #RefugeeDay

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Mindy Kaling on July 11, 2021 tagging @thechristinequinn. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: I SCREAMED when I was walking out of my dad and step-mom’s house and randomly saw @thechristinequinn on a break from shooting Selling Sunset on the sidewalk. It’s my favorite show on TV and not in like a “guilty pleasure” way; that show is SO GOOD. Christine is a fabulous real estate agent and new mom who sells $30 million dollar mansions in 7 inch Louboutins. Plus she keeps things spicy which is always nice! I love the whole cast and this made my year. Queen!
